dct_title_s: New Jersey topographic name sheet. Jersey City
dct_description_sm: New Jersey Geological Survey. Topographic Name Sheet. Jersey City (1928) Alternate title: Jersey City sheet. "Surveyed in 1887. Resurveyed in 1927." Relief shown by contours and spot elevation. Depths shown by soundings in feet.
